com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.errors

Class WOWZPlatformError

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.errors.WOWZError
      • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.errors.WOWZPlatformError

  • public class WOWZPlatformError
extends WOWZError
    The error code identifiers for the Android-specific API classes. Errors are normally reported as part of the WOWZStatus object returned by many of the API methods.
